Class CollisionStruct

  • java.lang.Object
    • model_classes.CollisionStruct

  • public class CollisionStruct
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by nilesh on 02/04/2017. This class was created so that when the collisionDetection algorithm is finished, if there is a collision then the moveBall function can use existing values instead of having to perform similar operations
